---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Chuleta Neovim">
  <main transition:animate="slide">
    ¡Holi! ¿Te apetece aprender a manejar el NeoVim como un@ campeon@? ¿Pues a
    qué esperas?
    <div id="botones">
      <a href="/guia-neovim/atajos">Atajos</a>
      <a href="/guia-neovim/comandos">Comandos</a>
      <a href="/guia-neovim/configuracion">Configuración</a>
      <a href="/guia-neovim/plugins">Plugins</a>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    margin: auto;
    padding: 1rem;
    width: 800px;
    max-width: calc(100% - 2rem);
    color: white;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    text-align: center;
  }

  #botones {
    margin-top: 2em;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;

    gap: 1.5em;

    @media (width < 720px) {
          flex-direction: column;
          width: 100%;
    }

    & a,
    & a:visited {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
      background-color: #44f;
      padding: 0.5em 1em;
      border-radius: 1em;
      box-shadow:
        0 0.25em 1.5em #226,
        0 0.25em 1.5em #226;
      transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
    }

    & a:hover {
      background-color: #66f;
      box-shadow:
        0 0.25em 1.5em #448,
        0 0.25em 1.5em #448;
    }
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1em;
  }
  .text-gradient {
    background-image: var(--accent-gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-size: 400%;
    background-position: 0%;
  }
  .instructions {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent-light), 25%);
    background: linear-gradient(
      rgba(var(--accent-dark), 66%),
      rgba(var(--accent-dark), 33%)
    );
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .instructions code {
    font-size: 0.8em;
    font-weight: bold;
    background: rgba(var(--accent-light), 12%);
    color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 0.3em 0.4em;
  }
  .instructions strong {
    color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
  }
  .link-card-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(24ch, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    padding: 0;
  }
</style>
